	   <tr><td colspan=2>Remember that weapons have a tendance to decress in value greatly.&nbsp;&nbsp;If your a level 20 monk and your fighting with a level 20 warrior, your using your fist, and he's using an exe axe, he is going to do more damage, becuase the exe axe was designed to be a 30 to 40th lvl weapon.  But with all the weapons from kunark it sells really cheap. Monk fist on the otherhand immprove as you go up in level. When you get to very high levels, and the warrior your grouped with is weilding a weapon that is more attuned to he's level you well be doing more damage.<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
